k Nicholson 饰）为了逃避监狱里的强制劳动，装作精神异常，被送进了精神病院，他的到来，给死气沉沉的精神病院带来了剧烈的冲击。 麦克要求看棒球比赛的电视转播，挑战了医院严格的管理制度，受到护士长拉契特（路易丝·弗莱彻 Louise Fletcher 饰）的百般阻挠；麦克带领病人出海捕鱼，振奋了他们的精神，却让院方头痛不已。院方为了惩处麦克胆大妄为、屡犯院规，决定将他永远留在疯人院。生性自由的麦克再也无法忍受疯人院的生活，他联合病友，高大的印第安人“酋长”，开始自己的计划：飞越疯人院。 本片获1975年第48届奥斯卡最佳影片，最佳男、女主角，最佳导演和最佳改编剧本五项大奖。主人公“不自由，毋宁死”的精神在当今社会仍有很大的现实意义。","vod_play_from":"bfzym3u8","vod_play_server":"","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"HD中字$https:\/\/s1.fengbao9.com\/video\/feiyuefengrenyuan\/11beb1e6c9b8\/index.m3u8","vod_down_from":"","vod_down_server":"","vod_down_note":"","vod_down_url":"","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type_name":"剧情片"},{"vod_id":139279,"type_id":26,"type_id_1":20,"group_id":0,"vod_name":"龙口走蛟","vod_sub":"","vod_en":"longkouzoujiao","vod_status":1,"vod_letter":"L","vod_color":"","vod_tag":"","vod_class":"剧情","vod_pic":"https:\/\/img.picbf.com\/upload\/vod\/20260324-1\/b2ea6cfbc516cd49f5029ca0df1b3b18.webp","vod_pic_thumb":"","vod_pic_slide":"","vod_pic_screenshot":"","vod_actor":"袁福福,黄允桐,许文广,梁超,王洪千,钱漪","vod_director":"董伟","vod_writer":"","vod_behind":"","vod_blurb":"龙口镇近来怪事不断，外乡人青云子和张不平游历至此，意外卷入神秘事件当中，他们最终揭开真相，守护了龙口镇的安宁。","vod_remarks":"更新至高清","vod_pubdate":"","vod_total":0,"vod_serial":"0","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"大陆","vod_lang":"国语","vod_year":"2026","vod_version":"","vod_state":"","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":0,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":0,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":458,"vod_hits_day":446,"vod_hits_week":774,"vod_hits_month":790,"vod_duration":"","vod_up":976,"vod_down":860,"vod_score":"7.0","vod_score_all":3185,"vod_score_num":455,"vod_time":"2026-03-24 12:46:24","vod_time_add":1774327573,"vod_time_hits":0,"vod_time_make":0,"vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":0,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"",